{"tid":1213543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港府若修訂逃犯條例   德國考慮廢止雙方引渡協定","createTime":"2019-06-13T01:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T02:03:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"be15bf114a1d984ca270b8f4ddd0b497e058eb54","tid":1213543,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:58:13.000Z","msg":"德國外交部官員表示，港府修訂逃犯條例引發大規模抗議，德支持示威民眾訴求。德國與香港簽有引渡協定，如果港府仍決定修訂逃犯條例，德國將考慮廢止與香港的引渡協定。<br />\n<br />\n德國外交部一名發言人12日表示，9日和12日兩天香港出現大規模抗議，可見多數香港民眾擔心法治受到侵蝕和香港從此失去自治，反對港府修訂逃犯條例。<br />\n<br />\n她強調，法律專家、業界人士和國際社會也持同樣的看法，德國曾聯合其它歐盟國家向港府清楚表達疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n德國總理梅克爾(Angela Merkel)的發言人表示，德國相當關注香港的情勢，香港的言論自由和法治有悠久的傳統，可是最近的情勢發展讓人想到基本法的相關規定。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，德國對多數示威群眾用和平方式表達意見表示肯定，呼籲所有參與的人保持冷靜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2023863\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2023863&d=OjLoGj31iMtRFsPqVtgEmrQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=f01e09b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2023863</a>"},{"pid":"8e3a85a7b694fecc8809c3894e3172cf10c7a69c","tid":1213543,"uid":108347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:02:11.000Z","msg":"又考慮，同聯合國遣責一樣有效心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca38dd89c05dece63de9f6285917acbe22515465","tid":1213543,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e3a85a7b694fecc8809c3894e3172cf10c7a69c","tid":1213543,"uid":108347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:02:11.000Z","msg":"又考慮，同聯合國遣責一樣有效心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:03:16.000Z","msg":"咪亂咁屌 最做得嘢係德國"}]}